      "rationale": "Three-level structured mesh refinement study performed on FDA pump geometry (coarse: 2.1M, medium: 6.8M, fine: 18.4M cells). GCI computed as 3.2% for NIH at 6 L/min, 3500 RPM operating point. Richardson extrapolation confirms asymptotic convergence ratio of 0.94. Achieved level exceeds MRL 2 requirement."
