      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump — same device class (centrifugal, Class II CPB), same fluid analog, overlapping operating envelope. COU device geometry differs in impeller blade angle and volute clearance; sensitivity analysis confirms hemolysis prediction methodology transfers with less than 8% additional uncertainty. Validation-to-COU relevance assessed as adequate for MRL 2."
