      "rationale": "Not formally assessed at MRL 2. Simulation setup reviewed by second analyst against documented simulation plan. Boundary conditions cross-checked against experimental data report. Post-processing scripts version-controlled and independently verified. Informal controls adequate for MRL 2 Class II submission."
