      "rationale": "Not formally assessed at MRL 2. SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published literature consensus for rotating blood pump flows. Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis damage model applied consistently with FDA-recognized approach. Model form uncertainty acknowledged but not quantified — acceptable at MRL 2 for Class II device."
